getting-started/installation.title: Installation
getting-started/installation.description: Get started with the Retreaver JavaScript API by installing it through your preferred package manager or using a CDN for direct browser usage.

intro.title: Welcome to Retreaver JavaScript API
intro.description: Welcome to the Retreaver JavaScript API documentation! This is a complete TypeScript rewrite of the original Retreaver JavaScript library, maintaining 100% backward compatibility while adding modern development features.
